    <h2>Marriage &amp; Family</h2>

    <h3>First Marriage (Pre-War)</h3>
    <p>Herman had a wife and children before WWII who perished during the Holocaust. No documentary records of their names have been found in the available sources. The 1959 ITS form lists his marital status "at the time of incarceration" as <em>ledig</em> (single), which may have been an administrative simplification or error, since family oral history confirms a pre-war family.</p>

